00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:49,980
You're the Supreme Deity of the Lunar Race.

563
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:51,220
Draw the Bow!

564
00:31:58,410 --> 00:31:59,780
Hurry, Xing Yue!

565
00:32:12,150 --> 00:32:13,340
Draw the Bow!

566
00:34:03,410 --> 00:34:06,200
Do you think you can kill me like this?

567
00:34:06,970 --> 00:34:07,780
No!

568
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:10,610
My Hidden Heart is still there.

569
00:34:11,250 --> 00:34:13,090
I will destroy the Divine Region,

570
00:34:13,090 --> 00:34:14,340
the world,

571
00:34:14,370 --> 00:34:15,870
and everything!

572
00:34:16,440 --> 00:34:18,420
None of you

573
00:34:18,989 --> 00:34:20,909
will get what you want!

574
00:34:50,120 --> 00:34:55,080
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

575
00:34:54,110 --> 00:34:55,570
The Divine Region is destroyed

576
00:34:55,570 --> 00:34:57,150
and the deities are falling.

577
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:58,730
Sealing this Hidden Heart

578
00:34:58,240 --> 00:35:03,870
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

579
00:34:59,240 --> 00:35:01,610
is the last thing I can do.

580
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:05,610
Jing Yuan!

581
00:35:06,530 --> 00:35:13,960
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

582
00:35:14,290 --> 00:35:15,660
Jing Yuan!

583
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:19,930
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

584
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:26,220
♫Across thousands of miles♫

585
00:35:31,010 --> 00:35:35,670
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

586
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:45,610
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

587
00:35:38,810 --> 00:35:39,810
Lunar Lord.

588
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:41,830
Lunar Lord!

589
00:35:46,740 --> 00:35:51,510
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

590
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:49,210
Lunar Lord.

591
00:35:57,840 --> 00:36:00,170
Hidden Lord's Hidden Heart is too strong.

592
00:36:00,220 --> 00:36:01,790
With my current power,

593
00:36:02,010 --> 00:36:04,110
I can't destroy him completely.

594
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:06,540
I can only rebuild the Stellar Formation

595
00:36:06,980 --> 00:36:08,440
to suppress the Hidden Heart

596
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:10,420
under the Lunar Hidden Sea.

597
00:36:11,030 --> 00:36:13,480
You've exhausted your power with your last arrow.

598
00:36:13,480 --> 00:36:15,280
To rebuild the Stellar Formation,

599
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:17,080
you have to sacrifice yourself.

600
00:36:17,490 --> 00:36:19,500
But if you die too,

601
00:36:19,810 --> 00:36:21,550
the Divine Region will be gone.

602
00:36:21,580 --> 00:36:23,260
The world is still here,

603
00:36:23,660 --> 00:36:24,720
no?

604
00:36:24,910 --> 00:36:26,910
As long as the Hidden Heart remains,

605
00:36:27,330 --> 00:36:29,620
its threat cannot be removed.

606
00:36:31,100 --> 00:36:32,450
My duty

607
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:34,300
is to suppress the Hidden Heart.

608
00:36:35,030 --> 00:36:36,370
Xiu Yan,

609
00:36:36,490 --> 00:36:38,150
your mission

610
00:36:38,610 --> 00:36:40,360
is to guard the Hidden Heart

611
00:36:40,380 --> 00:36:42,730
until the birth of the new Lunar Lord.

612
00:36:42,830 --> 00:36:43,630
No.

613
00:36:43,650 --> 00:36:44,400
No...

614
00:36:44,430 --> 00:36:45,500
Lunar Lord...

615
00:36:47,750 --> 00:36:48,590
Lunar Lord!

616
00:36:48,620 --> 00:36:49,510
No!

617
00:36:49,540 --> 00:36:50,580
No!

618
00:37:02,810 --> 00:37:06,780
♫The flowers flew away♫

619
00:37:10,510 --> 00:37:14,220
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

620
00:37:18,600 --> 00:37:25,440
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

621
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:32,120
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

622
00:37:44,970 --> 00:37:45,780
Remember.

623
00:37:46,710 --> 00:37:49,510
Only the full power of the Xing Yue Divine Bow

624
00:37:49,540 --> 00:37:51,870
can completely destroy the Hidden Heart.

625
00:37:51,950 --> 00:37:53,350
Remember.

626
00:37:53,370 --> 00:37:55,220
Bring everything

627
00:37:55,250 --> 00:37:56,890
back on track.

628
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:04,710
Lunar Lord!

629
00:38:03,650 --> 00:38:05,550
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

630
00:38:05,850 --> 00:38:07,850
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

631
00:38:07,910 --> 00:38:09,700
♫My love brought tears♫

632
00:38:09,950 --> 00:38:11,670
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

633
00:38:12,090 --> 00:38:13,650
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

634
00:38:14,130 --> 00:38:15,550
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

635
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:17,520
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

636
00:38:17,750 --> 00:38:19,490
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

637
00:38:19,980 --> 00:38:21,510
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

638
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:23,570
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

639
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:25,950
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

640
00:38:26,260 --> 00:38:27,840
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

641
00:38:27,070 --> 00:38:28,300
Lunar Lord...

642
00:38:28,160 --> 00:38:29,950
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

643
00:38:29,140 --> 00:38:32,370
I will guard the Lunar Hidden Sea and the Hidden Heart

644
00:38:30,220 --> 00:38:32,230
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

645
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:34,020
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

646
00:38:32,900 --> 00:38:34,730
with my life...

647
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:36,680
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

648
00:38:36,780 --> 00:38:38,750
till my final moments.

649
00:38:49,650 --> 00:38:52,580
The Hidden Heart would not destroy where it resided.

650
00:38:52,770 --> 00:38:54,200
So the Lunar Hidden Sea

651
00:38:54,500 --> 00:38:57,700
became the only surviving location of the Divine Region.

652
00:39:00,940 --> 00:39:01,750
Bai Shuo,

653
00:39:02,460 --> 00:39:04,270
you're the one I'm waiting for.

654
00:39:07,640 --> 00:39:08,470
No.

655
00:39:08,870 --> 00:39:11,400
Xing Yue, Jing Yuan, and Mo Li.

656
00:39:11,520 --> 00:39:13,300
They were already dead.

657
00:39:13,580 --> 00:39:15,560
Why can they still appear in the world?

658
00:39:15,560 --> 00:39:17,980
The heaven and earth gave birth to the Supreme Deities of Three Races.

659
00:39:17,980 --> 00:39:20,330
The bodies of the Supreme Deities may live and die,

660
00:39:20,330 --> 00:39:22,560
but the Divine Mantles will never disappear.

661
00:39:22,560 --> 00:39:24,300
As long as the Divine Mantles remain,

662
00:39:24,300 --> 00:39:26,030
they will be able to live again.

663
00:39:26,660 --> 00:39:27,920
However, no one knows

664
00:39:28,130 --> 00:39:30,440
how long that will take.

665
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:33,360
I'm already lucky that it only took

666
00:39:33,450 --> 00:39:35,180
60,000 years for me to meet you.

667
00:39:35,330 --> 00:39:37,360
But I met Jing Yuan ten years ago.

668
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:38,980
He was still alive back then.

669
00:39:39,010 --> 00:39:41,580
I cannot understand that either.

670
00:39:42,270 --> 00:39:44,420
Maybe only Jing Yuan

671
00:39:44,450 --> 00:39:46,280
knows the reason.

672
00:39:46,300 --> 00:39:47,700
What about Chong Zhao?

673
00:39:47,730 --> 00:39:49,000
You haven't answered me.

674
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:51,060
Why was the Hidden Lord reborn as an Eternal?

675
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:52,920
Because fate has been disrupted.

676
00:39:53,160 --> 00:39:54,750
The Fate of Heaven

677
00:39:54,770 --> 00:39:56,600
has been in chaos since

678
00:39:56,630 --> 00:39:58,430
the Divine Region was destroyed

679
00:39:58,660 --> 00:40:01,330
and couldn't control the whereabouts of your Divine Mantles.

680
00:40:01,330 --> 00:40:03,840
That's why Zhen Yu spent 60,000 years looking for

681
00:40:03,840 --> 00:40:06,580
all of you after escaping the Divine Region.

682
00:40:06,750 --> 00:40:07,670
Zhen Yu?

683
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:09,440
That black snake

684
00:40:09,670 --> 00:40:10,940
was Zhen Yu.

685
00:40:11,450 --> 00:40:13,770
Back then, his spiritual consciousness was not yet established,

686
00:40:13,770 --> 00:40:15,770
so he couldn't remember your faces.

687
00:40:15,970 --> 00:40:17,660
He only remembered

688
00:40:17,690 --> 00:40:19,220
his faith in the Hidden Lord

689
00:40:19,220 --> 00:40:20,640
and his mission to welcome him back.

690
00:40:20,640 --> 00:40:22,170
It's the same with Luan Zhu.

691
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:24,670
Thanks to the boundless life energy of the Soul Lotus,

692
00:40:24,670 --> 00:40:25,550
she survived

693
00:40:26,030 --> 00:40:28,150
and ended up on the Eastern Continent.

694
00:40:28,150 --> 00:40:30,150
She hated you for killing Jing Yuan.

695
00:40:30,300 --> 00:40:32,110
So she wanted to kill you too.

696
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:34,110
I once asked

697
00:40:34,700 --> 00:40:36,230
why she didn’t do it herself

698
00:40:36,790 --> 00:40:38,650
and made Chong Zhao do it instead.

699
00:40:38,700 --> 00:40:42,030
Because only a Supreme Deity can truly kill a Supreme Deity.

700
00:40:42,440 --> 00:40:43,880
60,000 years ago,

701
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:46,720
Xing Yue failed to truly kill Mo Li and Jing Yuan

702
00:40:46,920 --> 00:40:49,080
because her power was too weak.

703
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:51,500
If Chong Zhao really killed you that day,

704
00:40:51,750 --> 00:40:53,760
your Divine Mantle would have been destroyed

705
00:40:53,760 --> 00:40:55,840
and you'd never live again.

706
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:57,850
I see.

707
00:41:01,400 --> 00:41:02,400
That's not right.

708
00:41:02,970 --> 00:41:04,220
60,000 years ago,

709
00:41:04,250 --> 00:41:05,900
the Contemplation Stone was in your hands.

710
00:41:05,900 --> 00:41:07,740
You're the only deity who survived.

711
00:41:07,740 --> 00:41:09,780
But why did you say you were dead?

712
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:12,040
Why did the Contemplation Stone end up in Lanling?

713
00:41:12,040 --> 00:41:13,520
Hidden Lord's attack

714
00:41:13,550 --> 00:41:15,680
hurt me badly.

715
00:41:15,700 --> 00:41:17,340
At that time, I knew

716
00:41:17,370 --> 00:41:18,800
I had little time left.

717
00:41:18,830 --> 00:41:21,360
But I still had my promise to my Lunar Lord.

718
00:41:21,820 --> 00:41:24,950
I didn't want the Divine Region to end its legacy either.

719
00:41:25,090 --> 00:41:26,010
So,

720
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:28,100
I also went to the Eastern Continent.

721
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:32,310
I built a cave there

722
00:41:32,690 --> 00:41:34,750
and carved the secret techniques and history

723
00:41:34,750 --> 00:41:35,630
of the

724
00:41:35,650 --> 00:41:36,570
Divine Region

725
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:38,080
on the stone walls.

726
00:41:38,980 --> 00:41:40,420
At that time, I thought that

727
00:41:40,420 --> 00:41:41,900
maybe one day,

728
00:41:41,930 --> 00:41:44,130
a fated one would stumble upon this cave

729
00:41:44,420 --> 00:41:47,180
and witness the history and former glory

730
00:41:47,200 --> 00:41:48,400
of the Divine Region.

731
00:41:48,590 --> 00:41:49,960
In the Divine War,

732
00:41:50,130 --> 00:41:52,160
the Contemplation Stone went completely silent.

733
00:41:52,160 --> 00:41:54,570
And I sensed that the new Lunar Lord

734
00:41:54,590 --> 00:41:56,520
would be born in the Eastern Continent.

735
00:41:56,520 --> 00:41:58,240
So I gave the Contemplation Stone

736
00:41:58,240 --> 00:42:01,110
to the famous  Lanling Sect.

737
00:42:02,040 --> 00:42:03,440
I left a divine edict

738
00:42:03,850 --> 00:42:05,890
to let every sect leader of Lanling

739
00:42:05,950 --> 00:42:07,110
wait for and aid the girl

740
00:42:07,110 --> 00:42:09,640
who could activate the Contemplation Stone.

741
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:11,400
Unfortunately,

742
00:42:11,890 --> 00:42:14,480
when the secret was passed down to the current generation,

743
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:16,320
it was used by Jin Yao instead.

744
00:42:18,780 --> 00:42:20,110
After doing all that,

745
00:42:20,190 --> 00:42:22,050
I returned to the Lunar Hidden Sea

746
00:42:23,100 --> 00:42:25,500
and guarded the Hidden Heart without rest.

747
00:42:25,740 --> 00:42:26,530
Soon,

748
00:42:27,580 --> 00:42:29,240
I died from my serious injury.

749
00:42:30,610 --> 00:42:31,920
It was the protection power Lunar Lord

750
00:42:31,920 --> 00:42:33,920
left me in this Flaming Moon pendant

751
00:42:34,660 --> 00:42:36,880
that helped me maintain a thread of my divine soul

752
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:38,080
to this day.

753
00:42:38,670 --> 00:42:41,360
But why are you only telling me all this now?

754
00:42:41,900 --> 00:42:42,880
Why did you pretend

755
00:42:42,880 --> 00:42:44,610
to be my benefactor on purpose?

756
00:42:45,050 --> 00:42:46,030
Because at that time,

757
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:48,770
you were just a human who had never experienced the world.

758
00:42:48,770 --> 00:42:51,150
You didn't even know what Eternals and demons were,

759
00:42:51,150 --> 00:42:54,280
let alone understand what it means to protect the world.

760
00:42:54,340 --> 00:42:55,850
Becoming an Eternal to return the favor

761
00:42:55,850 --> 00:42:57,350
became your original intention,

762
00:42:57,350 --> 00:42:59,820
helping you overcome all obstacles along the way.

763
00:42:59,820 --> 00:43:00,740
Now,

764
00:43:01,060 --> 00:43:03,330
you've experienced a lot of life and death

765
00:43:03,330 --> 00:43:04,730
and developed your mind.

766
00:43:04,980 --> 00:43:06,880
You also possess the divine power

767
00:43:07,050 --> 00:43:08,750
to take on the responsibility now.

768
00:43:08,750 --> 00:43:10,360
If I were really a deity,

769
00:43:10,450 --> 00:43:12,220
why couldn't I be revived

770
00:43:12,250 --> 00:43:13,520
and save Fan Yue?

771
00:43:13,540 --> 00:43:14,940
I also didn't expect that

772
00:43:15,510 --> 00:43:18,170
Fan Yue would find the cave.

773
00:43:18,290 --> 00:43:19,890
The curse of the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal

774
00:43:19,890 --> 00:43:21,330
wasn’t part of my plan,

775
00:43:21,550 --> 00:43:23,350
and certainly not what I wanted.

776
00:43:23,580 --> 00:43:24,780
Now I can only help you

777
00:43:24,800 --> 00:43:26,630
protect his body.

778
00:43:26,670 --> 00:43:28,020
As for the rest,

779
00:43:28,220 --> 00:43:30,310
I can do nothing.

780
00:43:33,640 --> 00:43:35,000
But, Bai Shuo,

781
00:43:35,240 --> 00:43:36,990
this is not the time to be sad.

782
00:43:37,610 --> 00:43:39,470
I'm telling you everything today

783
00:43:39,670 --> 00:43:42,850
because the Lunar Hidden Sea can no longer suppress the Hidden Heart.

784
00:43:42,850 --> 00:43:44,180
Why?

785
00:43:44,200 --> 00:43:45,510
After 60,000 years,

786
00:43:46,020 --> 00:43:48,750
even the strongest divine power will disappear.

787
00:43:49,230 --> 00:43:52,360
Without Xing Yue and Jing Yuan's powers suppressing it,

788
00:43:52,530 --> 00:43:54,190
the Hidden Heart will escape,

789
00:43:54,320 --> 00:43:56,630
and the Lunar Hidden Sea will no longer exist.

790
00:43:56,630 --> 00:43:59,300
I can only use the Contemplation Stone in your body

791
00:43:59,300 --> 00:44:01,100
to keep the Hidden Heart for now.

792
00:44:01,450 --> 00:44:03,600
But this is not a long-term solution.

793
00:44:04,250 --> 00:44:05,170
Bai Shuo,

794
00:44:05,580 --> 00:44:07,750
you have to find the Xing Yue Divine Bow

795
00:44:07,970 --> 00:44:10,030
and completely destroy Hidden Heart

796
00:44:10,170 --> 00:44:12,510
to avoid the world-destroying catastrophe.

